            "text": "Macroeconomic Dynamics publishes research of the highest theoretical, empirical or quantitative sophistication. ",
            "section": "EDITORIAL POLICY"
        },
        {
            "text": "Papers of high quality are welcomed from all areas of advanced macroeconomics and allied fields, so long as the research is founded in a rigorous scientific approach. ",
