        },
        {
            "text": "Major advances in macroeconomics without immediate policy applications also are accepted, if they show potential for application in the future. ",
            "section": "EDITORIAL POLICY"
        },
        {
            "text": "Occasional book reviews, software reviews, announcements, conference proceedings and interviews are published.",
